    "body": "You have to use apm to install your module, like this:\n\n``` bash\ncd my-app\nvim package.json  # Adds your module to dependencies\napm install .\n```\n\n`apm install` doesn't work like `npm install` so this is the only right way to install native modules, any other way with `apm` could not work. See the [docs](https://github.com/atom/atom-shell/blob/master/docs/tutorial/use-native-node-modules.md) for more.\n"
